{"tid":666055,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[返上去團聚啦]海南出招搶人才　港澳台居民可申請永久居留","createTime":"2018-05-15T13:50:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T02:52:54.000Z","uid":51271,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"75f71b0c268ef896343278049d301e229c42e4a4","tid":666055,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T13:50:27.000Z","msg":"上面大把景呀，單程證無撚柒用，移民去海南啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180515/bkn-20180515172414599-0515_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180515%2Fbkn-20180515172414599-0515_00822_001.html&d=bL7GQT81pL1CdRmlcKQKd%2BI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=598ae760\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180515/bkn-20180515172414599-0515_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n海南省早前公布將建設自由貿易試驗區及自由貿易港，而為吸引來自世界各地的精英，海南省委周日（13日）通過《百萬人才進海南行動計劃（2018&mdash;2025年）》，讓具有專上學歷、中級以上專業技術職稱、技師或以上職業資格的人才能在當地工作及落戶。該計劃又開放予港澳台民眾申請，符合標準的人才及其家人可直接申請永久居留。<br />\n<br />\n符合資格者在當地買樓時，享有與當地居民同等的待遇。在人才住房保障方面，海南將為引進的領軍人才、傑出人才及大師級人才，以免租方式提供150至200平方米的公寓。而截至周一（14日），已有120人在宣傳活動現場申請落戶，81人獲發「准予遷入證明」。<br />\n<br />\n該計劃又提到，相關人才在當地全職工作滿5年後，可贈予80%產權；滿8年贈予100%產權。40歲以下全日制大學生、碩士生、其他類高層次人才、拔尖人才每日可獲1500至5000元人民幣的租房補貼，共發放3年。<br />\n<br />\n另為降低人才直系親屬的就學門檻，在行政安排上予以便利，並為其引進國內外名校及國際學校，以提高教育水平。"},{"pid":"052b2f87e5fbc6cb0d7f9220ddbee5dd928ec33c","tid":666055,"uid":59695,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T13:57:20.000Z","msg":"40歲以下全日制大學生、碩士生、其他類高層次人才、拔尖人才每日可獲1500至5000元人民幣的租房補貼，共發放3年<br />\n<br />\n五毛福音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52eca16c12f9f7f317dcc50372677c88bb0609c6","tid":666055,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T14:08:10.000Z","msg":"我去瓦努阿圖唔好?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e770c1b361e23f41ae8aa608d68087023daa2bbc","tid":666055,"uid":48277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T14:09:05.000Z","msg":"熱到仆街"},{"pid":"a99daae421c721957c8e5330e99b056efbbb9209","tid":666055,"uid":48458,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"75f71b0c268ef896343278049d301e229c42e4a4","tid":666055,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T13:50:27.000Z","msg":"上面大把景呀，單程證無撚柒用，移民去海南啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180515/bkn-20180515172414599-0515_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180515%2Fbkn-20180515172414599-0515_00822_001.html&d=bL7GQT81pL1CdRmlcKQKd%2BI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=598ae760\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180515/bkn-20180515172414599-0515_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n海南省早前公布將建設自由貿易試驗區及自由貿易港，而為吸引來自世界各地的精英，海南省委周日（13日）通過《百萬人才進海南行動計劃（2018&mdash;2025年）》，讓具有專上學歷、中級以上專業技術職稱、技師或以上職業資格的人才能在當地工作及落戶。該計劃又開放予港澳台民眾申請，符合標準的人才及其家人可直接申請永久居留。<br